# -*- mode: gitignore; -*-
# Consolidated canonical ignore file for dotfiles repository.
#
# Compliant with [/Users/s-a-c/dotfiles/dot-config/ai/guidelines.md](/Users/s-a-c/dotfiles/dot-config/ai/guidelines.md) v50b6b88e7dea25311b5e28879c90b857ba9f1c4b0bc974a72f6b14bc68d54f49
#
# Purpose:
# - Minimize noise (OS/editor cruft, build artifacts, caches)
# - Exclude secret material and environment configuration directories (any .env/ folder)
# - Support future automated secret scanning by preventing accidental additions
#
# Sections:
#  1. OS / System
#  2. Other VCS Residue
#  3. Editors & IDEs
#  4. Language & Tool Artifacts
#  5. Backups / Temp / Logs
#  6. Secrets / Credentials / Infra State
#  7. Project-Specific / Custom
#
# NOTE:
# - In .gitignore, a leading slash anchors to repo root; no regex anchors like ^ are used.
# - Pattern `.env/` (without leading slash) matches any directory named `.env` at any depth.

###############################################################################
# 1. OS / SYSTEM
###############################################################################
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
